until 10:30 at night.

13:03.110 --> 13:04.030
Where is that racket?

13:04.280 --> 13:05.280
I bet it’s down this hallway.

13:05.530 --> 13:07.070
In the basement.
I think it’s in the basement.

13:07.200 --> 13:08.660
It’s not there.
It’s in the base--

13:21.460 --> 13:23.470
You gotta be kidding me.

13:29.600 --> 13:30.560
Seriously?

13:31.390 --> 13:32.560
I’m sorry.

13:33.930 --> 13:35.850
Stan, I promised
you’d drop this off months ago.

13:38.150 --> 13:39.610
This isn’t good for you.

13:40.400 --> 13:41.650
It’s been a while now.

13:44.070 --> 13:45.150
