Hey!

15:30.970 --> 15:31.970
Is Nathan Williams present?

15:32.340 --> 15:33.640
Yes, he’s right here.

15:33.850 --> 15:35.260
Nathan Williams,
you’re under arrest.

15:35.470 --> 15:36.270
Turn around.

15:36.520 --> 15:37.520
Hands behind your back.

15:37.980 --> 15:38.980
You have the
right to remain silent.

15:39.310 --> 15:40.480
Anything you say,
can, and will be

15:40.600 --> 15:42.020
