15:44.400 --> 15:45.440
I’m not a bad guy.

15:45.570 --> 15:46.440
I know.

15:46.570 --> 15:47.940
-...rights that I’ve read you.
-Yes.

15:48.240 --> 15:49.530
In hearing these rights,
Do you wish to talk to --

15:49.650 --> 15:51.110
Where are you taking him?

15:52.990 --> 15:53.870
It’s okay.

16:16.850 --> 16:19.220
Turn to your right.

16:22.440 --> 16:23.440
Strip.

16:30.320 --> 16:31.530
All the way.

16:39.080 --> 16:40.500
You’re in trouble,
Nathan.

16:41.660 --> 16:43.120
Who was with you?

16:44.960 --> 16:45.960
No one.

16:47.540 --> 16:48.670
You did this alone?

16:50.670 --> 16:51.920
A witness said
they saw someone,

16:52.050 --> 16:52.840
maybe two other peo--.

16:52.970 --> 16:54.050
I was on my own.

16:58.890 --> 17:00.060
You get to make
one phone call.

17:00.430 --> 17:01.180
Let’s go.

17:03.350 --> 17:05.480
I don--I don’t have
anyone to call.

17:07.690 --> 17:09.270
Oh, sorry.
Morning, Barnaby.

17:09.650 --> 17:12.030
Nadine, Paul, Chris, Madison.

17:13.030 --> 17:13.860
