17:14.570 --> 17:15.780
I know, John,
but what did he do?

17:15.950 --> 17:17.490
Hey, does
anyone know if Nathan--

17:19.200 --> 17:20.160
It was burglary.

17:20.490 --> 17:21.410
Someone’s home?

17:21.660 --> 17:23.660
It was West Barnes’
appliance store in New Holland.

17:24.670 --> 17:26.710
Did they have to arrest him
in front of the whole school?

17:27.080 --> 17:29.250
