19:11.440 --> 19:16.070
I’m here to
see Nathan Williams.

19:16.440 --> 19:17.490
Are you family?

19:18.610 --> 19:20.240
No. No, I’m his teacher.

19:20.860 --> 19:22.490
Can’t let you back
unless you’re family.

19:23.240 --> 19:24.370
Well, at Garden Spot,
we like to think

19:24.490 --> 19:25.990
of all of our
students as family.

19:26.580 --> 19:29.290
